title: Venetian Mirror PL-08-VDS-01
desc: Venetian mirrors are made up of long lines and sweeping arches. The polished edges and mirrored borders are heavenly and pristine. They're available in a variety of shapes, including rectangles, ovals and circles. Some even have delicate etching around the glass' perimeter. The feminine rosettes that adorn each Venetian mirror are gracefully ornate. Venetian mirrors are well loved for their attention to detail without ever becoming unbalanced or gaudy. One of these timeless pieces will look lovely gracing the wall of your bedroom, bathroom or living room.

title: "OLIVER" Designer Wall and Bathroom Mirror
desc:
Mirror steel "Oliver".
The feedback received in time from the traditional mirror Olimpo in extra-transparent methacrylate, inspired the creation of a new extra reflective steel version, expanding the range of this special collecion.
Its design has of a new facelift that sees the size increased to 150 cm in height and re-design of the friezes for the baroque style evocative frame. The oval mirror positioned in the steel structure is beveled, and increases in size.
OLIVER surprises his audience, from the simplicity of the idea behind the design can be a very distinctive mirrors, playing with the color of the background on which it is placed and interacting through multiple reflections with the environments.
Design and Manufactured by Riflessi, Italy.

title: "Mito" Hammered frame Designer wall Mirror
desc:
Creativity, Handcrafting, Technique: This is the winning formula that makes the 'Mito' collection the leading actor and the most distinguish in the history of RIFLESSI mirrors. The frames are individually hand modeled. The traditional processing follows the special features of a perticular aluminum technologically treated to make the best color, shine and shape. Each mirror MITO is therefore an art work unique and unrepeatable. Also available with frame lacquered in white or any RAL range color (on demand) and with different sizez and shapes: Square, Rectanglar, Round, Midi and Mini; Mito collection is by nature a family mirror achieving functional and decorative objectives as well as inspiring the creativity anf freedom of placement in different interiors concepts.

Manufactured by Riflessi, Italy

title: "Mito Novecento" Designer Wall and Bathroom Mirror
desc:
Wall mirror "Mito Novecento".
Mito 900 is a further development in the top-range mito collection, unique handmade art works. The design is inspired by the big classic mirrors of the past century.
Mito ‘900 has a classical style but at the same time is a link between the past and modernity, thanks to the blending of a romantic oval shape and the high-tech yet handmade aluminum frame.
Mito ‘900 has a distinct personality that fits in environments with character and elegance both classic, contemporary or wisely mixed.
Design and Manufactured by Riflessi, Italy.
